I was having drinks.

16:47.528 --> 16:51.401
It's not my first,
because I'm an adult human.

16:51.401 --> 16:52.794
I drink alcohol.

16:52.794 --> 16:54.796
My stomach is so warm.

16:54.796 --> 16:57.712
