Ohh, ugh.

17:20.648 --> 17:22.780
I did it.

17:22.780 --> 17:24.478
Why do I feel like fighting?

17:25.696 --> 17:27.307
Keep it.

17:27.307 --> 17:29.570
What?

17:29.570 --> 17:31.833
Mom, sorry.

17:34.488 --> 17:36.098
Where is he?

17:36.098 --> 17:38.840
Is your mother a beaver?

17:38.840 --> 17:45.238
Because damn, girl.

