who's not adopted,

17:46.935 --> 17:48.371
it's hard to understand.

17:48.371 --> 17:52.114
It's-- you know your story.

17:52.114 --> 17:55.683
It starts way back somewhere
and-- and moves forward

17:55.683 --> 17:57.946
like chapters in a novel.

17:57.946 --> 17:59.861
And at some point,
you show up in it.

17:59.861 --> 18:01.950
But me, it's like
the pages before me

18:01.950 --> 18:04.431
were torn out of the book,
and Mary Ellen has them.

18:04.431 --> 18:07.564
And she's gonna sell them
to you, and that's wrong.

18:07.564 --> 18:11.133
And if you pay her,
she's never gonna go away.

18:11.133 --> 18:13.440
She's gonna keep coming back.

18:13.440 --> 18:16.095
And that would be--

18:16.095 --> 18:17.531
Bad.

18:17.531 --> 18:18.575
Right.

18:18.575 --> 18:20.621
There you are.

18:20.621 --> 18:23.798
Are either one of you going
to kick me in the nipple?

18:23.798 --> 18:26.540
I mean, I wasn't, but now
it's all I can think about.

18:26.540 --> 18:27.889
What happened?

18:27.889 --> 18:30.283
I heard you got banned
from Mama Sap's.

18:30.283 --> 18:31.240
What?

18:31.240 --> 18:33.721
The cheese comes from her toes.

18:33.721 --> 18:35.375
Stay away!

18:35.375 --> 18:38.160
<i>This is what the little shit
meant by worse than death.</i>

18:38.160 --> 18:41.120
<i>He is going to
destroy my life here.</i>

18:41.120 --> 18:42.947
What's going on with you?

18:42.947 --> 18:47.038
