a strong enough parent.

18:47.038 --> 18:50.781
<i>I'm going to do some
nipple kicking of my own.</i>

18:57.484 --> 18:58.876
Mom.

18:58.876 --> 19:00.095
Hey, how is he?

19:00.095 --> 19:03.272
Not good.
Look at him.

19:03.272 --> 19:05.100
His heart stopped.

19:05.100 --> 19:08.190
He just keeled over, spilled
his M&Ms all over the place,

19:08.190 --> 19:10.236
and then they had
to start him up

19:10.236 --> 19:12.586
right there in the hotel room.

19:12.586 --> 19:14.109
It was awful.

19:14.109 --> 19:17.721
What-- what are you
doing in Colorado?

19:17.721 --> 19:18.983
My cousin Louisa's birthday.

19:18.983 --> 19:20.420
You remember her.

19:20.420 --> 19:22.248
No, sorry.

19:22.248 --> 19:23.423
Cousin Louisa?

19:23.423 --> 19:24.467
Yeah, I heard you.

19:24.467 --> 19:26.295
I just don't remember.

19:26.295 --> 19:27.775
Cousin Louisa.

19:27.775 --> 19:28.819
I don't know her.

19:28.819 --> 19:29.951
Shh.

19:29.951 --> 19:32.083
You'll disturb your father.

19:33.650 --> 19:37.001
I sure wish I could find that
nurse with the ice chips.

19:37.001 --> 19:38.916
I think we can wait
until he wakes up.

19:38.916 --> 19:41.049
They're not for him.

19:42.529 --> 19:44.008
Oh.

19:44.008 --> 19:47.838
