gifted program I was in.

28:31.840 --> 28:34.974
Everyone was older,
and they were all so smart.

28:34.974 --> 28:39.282
And I was just average.

28:39.282 --> 28:41.023
I've never been average.

28:41.023 --> 28:42.764
It's like you.

28:42.764 --> 28:44.984
Here, you're smarter than most
humans, but on your planet,

28:44.984 --> 28:46.376
you're probably really dumb.

28:46.376 --> 28:49.292
No, I was
exceptional there, too.

28:49.292 --> 28:52.861
A C student at best.

28:52.861 --> 28:54.558
Ah!

28:54.558 --> 28:56.778
Oh, my gosh, baby, you're here.

28:56.778 --> 28:58.127
Bridget.

28:58.127 --> 28:59.955
Oh, I really missed you.

28:59.955 --> 29:02.784
You were probably so
scared, but I'm here now.

29:02.784 --> 29:05.221
Everything is OK.

29:09.965 --> 29:11.445
You killed him!

29:11.445 --> 29:14.753
No, we killed him.

29:22.499 --> 29:23.457
You killed your baby.

29:23.457 --> 29:24.545
No.

29:24.545 --> 29:26.199
Well, he started it.

29:26.199 --> 29:27.635
He was going to kill me.

29:27.635 --> 29:29.942
I don't even have a child,
and I know not killing

29:29.942 --> 29:31.378
it is, like, the main thing.

29:31.378 --> 29:32.814
He was broken.

29:32.814 --> 29:34.990
He didn't love me anymore.

29:34.990 --> 29:36.557
He doesn't have to love you.

29:36.557 --> 29:37.950
You're supposed to love him.

29:37.950 --> 29:40.039
That does not sound
like a good deal to me.

29:40.039 --> 29:42.258
But--

29:53.661 --> 29:55.706
Bridget?

29:55.706 --> 29:57.230
Bridget, you're back.

29:57.230 --> 29:59.319
Molecular genetic
regeneration.

29:59.319 --> 30:03.149
One of Bridget's bits
found a piece of DNA.

30:03.149 --> 30:05.412
I am very impressed
with my baby.

30:09.895 --> 30:11.722
Oh, look at that.

30:11.722 --> 30:14.334
Bridget found some more DNA.

30:14.334 --> 30:17.511
So many.

30:17.511 --> 30:18.947
Impressive.

30:20.688 --> 30:23.125
<i>♪ A child arrived
just the other day ♪</i>

30:23.125 --> 30:26.912
So do you, like,
never vacuum?

30:26.912 --> 30:28.609
What's wrong, Harry?

30:28.609 --> 30:29.784
Didn't you miss us?

30:29.784 --> 30:31.220
You should run.

30:31.220 --> 30:33.179
<i>♪ Learned to walk
while I was away ♪</i>

30:33.179 --> 30:34.963
<i>♪ And he was talking
before I knew it ♪</i>

30:34.963 --> 30:39.620
<i>♪ And as he grew, he'd say,
I'm gonna be like you, Dad ♪</i>

30:39.620 --> 30:41.013
I got this.

30:41.013 --> 30:43.493
<i>♪ You know I'm
gonna be like you ♪</i>

30:43.493 --> 30:45.191
Oh!

30:45.191 --> 30:47.802
<i>♪ And the cat's in the
cradle and the silver spoon ♪</i>

30:47.802 --> 30:51.153
<i>♪ Little boy blue
and the man in the moon ♪</i>

30:51.153 --> 30:52.807
<i>♪ When you
coming home, Dad? ♪</i>

30:52.807 --> 30:57.290
<i>♪ I don't know when,
but we'll get together then ♪</i>

30:57.290 --> 30:59.901
<i>♪ You know we'll have
a good time then ♪</i>

31:03.209 --> 31:05.167
Ah!

31:07.387 --> 31:09.258
Ahh!

