<i>♪ My son turned ten
just the other day ♪</i>

31:12.087 --> 31:13.915
<i>♪ He said,
thanks for the ball, Dad ♪</i>

31:13.915 --> 31:15.177
<i>♪ Come on, let's play</i>

31:15.177 --> 31:16.787
<i>♪ Can you teach me to throw?</i>

31:16.787 --> 31:18.137
<i>♪ I said, not today</i>

31:18.137 --> 31:20.704
<i>♪ I got a lot to do</i>

31:21.792 --> 31:22.837
Ah!

31:22.837 --> 31:23.925
You bastard.

31:23.925 --> 31:27.537
I let you use the bathroom.

31:27.537 --> 31:31.759
<i>♪ You know
I'm gonna be like him ♪</i>

31:31.759 --> 31:35.458
<i>♪ And the cat's in the
cradle and the silver spoon ♪</i>

31:35.458 --> 31:38.592
<i>♪ Little boy blue
and the man on the moon ♪</i>

31:38.592 --> 31:42.726
Is it really you?

31:42.726 --> 31:44.032
I ought to slap you.

31:44.032 --> 31:47.644
Why do you have teeth?

31:59.134 --> 32:00.919
Maybe it just
knocked him out.

32:02.050 --> 32:05.967
Knocked him out his skin, maybe.

32:05.967 --> 32:07.229
He was taken up.

32:09.188 --> 32:09.971
Up?

32:09.971 --> 32:11.451
Like to heaven?

32:11.451 --> 32:13.366
No, she means like
with one of those claws.

32:13.366 --> 32:15.063
The military has
them on helicopters.

32:15.063 --> 32:16.325
It's like the
ones in the arcade,

32:16.325 --> 32:17.718
except they're
not rigged so you

32:17.718 --> 32:18.980
can never win the damn koala.

32:18.980 --> 32:21.200
That's not what I mean.

32:21.200 --> 32:22.592
I mean by an alien spaceship.

32:22.592 --> 32:23.680
No.

32:23.680 --> 32:25.291
OK, just stop it, all right?

32:25.291 --> 32:26.683
I don't want to hear any more
of this ridiculous

32:26.683 --> 32:28.207
alien shit, OK?

32:28.207 --> 32:30.600
Now if you'll excuse me, I'm
gonna go look for drag marks

32:30.600 --> 32:32.994
from a top secret invisible
military claw chopper.

32:41.002 --> 32:45.180
You really think
this was aliens?

32:45.180 --> 32:50.142
You hit him going 50 miles
per hour, and now he's gone.

32:50.142 --> 32:53.188
There's no footprints,
no blood trail.

32:53.188 --> 32:56.887
And did you see
or hear a helicopter?

32:56.887 --> 33:00.021
I think Joseph is an alien.

33:00.021 --> 33:02.850
They're real, Ben.

33:02.850 --> 33:05.505
Aliens are real,
and they abduct people,

33:05.505 --> 33:07.028
and they don't remember.

33:25.264 --> 33:26.526
Ah.

33:26.526 --> 33:30.051
Ahh! Ahh!

33:40.453 --> 33:43.369
What is that?

33:43.369 --> 33:45.414
Oh.

33:45.414 --> 33:50.637
Is that-- who put
a booger in my home?

33:57.209 --> 34:00.125
Max.

34:00.125 --> 34:04.085
I tried to kill
him so many times.

34:04.085 --> 34:05.478
I do not want
to kill him anymore.

34:05.478 --> 34:07.610
So stick him in a pod
and send him away.

34:07.610 --> 34:08.916
That's what you like to do.

34:08.916 --> 34:10.657
I did that for you.

34:10.657 --> 34:12.267
You did it for you.

34:12.267 --> 34:15.053
No, I had work to do.

34:15.053 --> 34:18.926
The future of the entire
planet depends on me.

34:18.926 --> 34:19.927
I don't care.

34:19.927 --> 34:21.015
I'm a baby.

34:21.015 --> 34:22.930
I needed you.

34:22.930 --> 34:24.540
You shoved me
in that spaceship.

34:24.540 --> 34:27.152
I thought we were
going together.

34:27.152 --> 34:29.719
<i>I needed my father.</i>

34:29.719 --> 34:33.071
Daddy.

34:33.071 --> 34:34.420
<i>I abandoned you.</i>

34:34.420 --> 34:36.770
You were abandoned
by the one you love,

34:36.770 --> 34:38.728
just like I was by Heather.

34:40.687 --> 34:42.645
I am sorry.

34:42.645 --> 34:45.039
Because your girlfriend
broke up with you?

34:45.039 --> 34:46.606
No, because--

34:46.606 --> 34:48.869
<i>What is this?</i>

34:48.869 --> 34:52.177
<i>I thought it had gone
forever when Heather left me.</i>

34:52.177 --> 34:56.137
<i>But it came back.</i>

34:56.137 --> 34:58.052
because I love you.

35:00.620 --> 35:01.621
Oh.

35:02.839 --> 35:05.668
<i>Babies do not care
what anyone feels.</i>

35:05.668 --> 35:09.629
<i>They only want to be taken
care of, to be loved...</i>

35:14.286 --> 35:16.462
<i>And to know there is
someone out there who will</i>

35:16.462 --> 35:21.206
<i>find a way to protect them.</i>

35:21.206 --> 35:23.164
<i>No matter what it takes.</i>

35:45.839 --> 35:47.145
Hey.

35:47.145 --> 35:48.494
I know it's late.

35:48.494 --> 35:49.495
Yeah.

35:49.495 --> 35:50.931
What's going on?

35:50.931 --> 35:53.673
I just wanted to say
that, um, I'm happy for you

35:53.673 --> 35:55.588
and your girlfriend.

35:55.588 --> 35:57.198
I don't remember her name,
but I hope

35:57.198 --> 36:00.201
that she has a great life
and that you

36:00.201 --> 36:01.202
have a great life.

36:01.202 --> 36:03.683
But I've got to go.

36:03.683 --> 36:06.120
D'Arcy, are you OK?

36:06.120 --> 36:07.165
Come inside.

36:07.165 --> 36:08.427
I'm not on anything.

36:08.427 --> 36:10.037
Just my dad's in the hospital.

36:10.037 --> 36:12.518
He's gonna be fine, but he--

36:12.518 --> 36:17.610
he's-- he's proud of me,
and he says I'm built to do

36:17.610 --> 36:20.395
something great,
something big,

36:20.395 --> 36:24.051
and I think I know
what that is now.

36:24.051 --> 36:26.575
And if you never
see me again, I just

36:26.575 --> 36:30.231
wanted you to know that I
know that you cared about me,

36:30.231 --> 36:36.803
and I messed it up,
and that--

36:36.803 --> 36:40.067
yeah, OK, but you're
gonna be proud of me, too.

36:40.067 --> 36:42.765
So bye.

36:42.765 --> 36:44.506
D'Arcy.

36:44.506 --> 36:49.337
D'Arcy!

37:36.863 --> 37:38.343
Good morning!

37:38.343 --> 37:40.693
Ah, good morning.

37:40.693 --> 37:43.565
I brought this for you.

37:43.565 --> 37:47.830
You can put it on your desk.

37:47.830 --> 37:51.312
Oh, that is so sweet.

37:51.312 --> 37:54.750
But no.

37:54.750 --> 37:56.143
I have some good news.

37:56.143 --> 37:57.623
OK.

37:57.623 --> 38:00.190
I stayed up late last night,
and I finished the bomb!

38:00.190 --> 38:02.192
Harry, shh.

38:02.192 --> 38:04.369
I stayed up late last night.

38:04.369 --> 38:06.675
That's not the part.

38:06.675 --> 38:07.807
Never mind.

38:07.807 --> 38:10.375
That is great news.

38:10.375 --> 38:15.554
The, uh, lady general is
going to be coming to my cabin

38:15.554 --> 38:18.644
later to hear my plan.

38:18.644 --> 38:22.604
I could use more information
about the Greys' ship layout,

38:22.604 --> 38:24.780
but I may have
enough to proceed.

38:24.780 --> 38:26.434
Thank God.
I'm glad.

38:26.434 --> 38:27.870
Mm-hmm.

38:27.870 --> 38:30.133
I'm also glad that you
have Bridget back, too.

38:30.133 --> 38:34.486
I thought I was doing
what was best for him.

38:34.486 --> 38:37.271
But I was selfish.

38:37.271 --> 38:38.968
It was for me.

38:38.968 --> 38:41.362
You know, it's not
always easy to know.

38:41.362 --> 38:43.973
Yes, like you with Jay.

38:43.973 --> 38:45.148
Why do people
keep saying this?

38:45.148 --> 38:47.194
I did not have selfish reasons.

38:47.194 --> 38:53.461
No, you made a difficult
choice to give Jay away.

38:53.461 --> 38:55.245
That was good.

38:55.245 --> 38:56.377
Thank you.

38:56.377 --> 38:58.640
I meant you are
selfish with Jay now.

38:58.640 --> 39:00.990
What?

39:00.990 --> 39:04.864
Yeah, I'm gonna
put that right there.

39:04.864 --> 39:07.040
It looks so good.

39:13.089 --> 39:14.439
Hi.

39:14.439 --> 39:16.397
Sorry, I--

39:16.397 --> 39:19.400
I don't have
an appointment, but I--

39:19.400 --> 39:22.055
I have something
in the back of my neck.

39:22.055 --> 39:25.972
And I need you to
take it out right now.

39:25.972 --> 39:28.017
<i>It is a Grey implant.</i>

39:28.017 --> 39:29.584
<i>They are taking
Mayor Snowflake,</i>

39:29.584 --> 39:31.543
<i>so it is not surprising
that they are also</i>

39:31.543 --> 39:33.545
<i>taking Mrs. Mayor Snowflake.</i>

39:33.545 --> 39:35.155
<i>This is excellent.</i>

39:35.155 --> 39:37.984
<i>I can use her to get
intel about the Grey ship.</i>

39:37.984 --> 39:38.985
You seem upset.

39:38.985 --> 39:40.987
I can calm you.

39:40.987 --> 39:42.380
Have you ever been hypnotized?

39:48.037 --> 39:50.823
You are on the Greys' ship.

39:50.823 --> 39:53.086
Tell me everything you see.

39:53.086 --> 39:56.306
They're--
they're walking with me.

39:56.306 --> 39:57.699
<i>Yes.</i>

39:57.699 --> 39:59.832
<i>Yes, how many doors are there?</i>

39:59.832 --> 40:01.442
<i>Are their guards?</i>

40:01.442 --> 40:02.661
And how many?

40:02.661 --> 40:03.836
Where is she?

40:03.836 --> 40:05.664
<i>Let me see her.</i>

40:05.664 --> 40:07.535
Who is she?

40:07.535 --> 40:09.189
Is it a guard?

40:09.189 --> 40:12.410
A leader?

40:12.410 --> 40:13.715
There she is.

40:16.588 --> 40:18.328
Oh, my sweet.

40:18.328 --> 40:19.286
There's my baby.

40:19.286 --> 40:20.679
Yeah.

40:20.679 --> 40:24.465
<i>The little bastards
took Mrs. Mayor's child.</i>

40:24.465 --> 40:26.249
<i>She would not
like to know that.</i>

40:26.249 --> 40:28.556
<i>It would make her
angry and sad.</i>

40:28.556 --> 40:33.474
<i>I will make sure she does not
remember it when she wakes up.</i>

40:33.474 --> 40:35.084
How many are there?

40:35.084 --> 40:36.869
Do they have weapons?

40:36.869 --> 40:39.437
Oh, I love her so much.

40:42.091 --> 40:44.485
They want me to bond with her.

40:44.485 --> 40:46.356
<i>I want her home--</i>

40:46.356 --> 40:47.357
It's all right.

40:47.357 --> 40:49.751
<i>with me.</i>

40:49.751 --> 40:51.013
<i>This is no help.</i>

40:51.013 --> 40:53.494
<i>She is too focused
on her baby.</i>

40:53.494 --> 40:55.148
<i>I understand.</i>

40:55.148 --> 40:57.803
<i>I would be so sad if I did
not know that my baby existed.</i>

40:57.803 --> 41:01.154
<i>And I realize now that
happiness is not just getting</i>

41:01.154 --> 41:04.810
<i>love but getting to love.</i>

41:04.810 --> 41:09.989
When I snap my fingers,
you will wake up,

41:09.989 --> 41:16.125
and you will
remember everything.

41:17.866 --> 41:21.566
3, 2, 1.

41:27.920 --> 41:31.184
Oh, no!

41:42.195 --> 41:46.591
I love you, but this is
the right thing for you.

41:46.591 --> 41:50.377
I've loved every second
of getting to act

41:50.377 --> 41:52.248
like a mom to you.

41:52.248 --> 41:55.121
But I love it so much
that I've skipped over all

41:55.121 --> 41:58.124
the parts of knowing how.

41:58.124 --> 42:00.430
I'm glad I could be part
of your learning process.

42:00.430 --> 42:02.128
I know you're mad,
but you should

42:02.128 --> 42:04.347
be here right now with
the people who raised you,

42:04.347 --> 42:06.045
and you know it.

42:06.045 --> 42:09.352
It would have been nice if it
was my choice for once, Asta.

42:09.352 --> 42:11.529
I'm a person.

42:11.529 --> 42:12.791
I should have a say.

42:12.791 --> 42:14.314
I agree.

42:14.314 --> 42:17.491
We never even talked
about the whole thing.

42:17.491 --> 42:18.971
The whole?

42:18.971 --> 42:22.322
How you kept this a secret
from me my entire life.

42:22.322 --> 42:23.541
Right.

42:23.541 --> 42:26.326
How you hired me
just to be near me,

42:26.326 --> 42:28.850
and you still didn't tell me.

42:28.850 --> 42:32.593
I-- I was afraid.

42:36.989 --> 42:42.560
I finally got everything
I ever wanted.

42:42.560 --> 42:46.564
It was just so delicate and
fragile that if I looked at it

42:46.564 --> 42:48.348
the wrong way or
breathed on it too hard,

42:48.348 --> 42:51.003
it would break and be gone.

42:51.003 --> 42:54.223
Same.

42:54.223 --> 42:57.487
It was messed up.

42:57.487 --> 42:58.532
And I am sorry.

42:58.532 --> 43:01.491
And you are right.

43:01.491 --> 43:05.365
Let's talk about it.

43:05.365 --> 43:07.846
Now?

43:07.846 --> 43:11.632
No.

43:11.632 --> 43:14.504
That's what the rest
of our lives are for.

43:14.504 --> 43:16.028
Oh.

43:16.028 --> 43:18.030
Oh.

43:20.119 --> 43:21.337
Oh, retainer.

43:21.337 --> 43:22.382
Oh.

43:22.382 --> 43:23.557
Thanks.

43:26.342 --> 43:28.649
God.

43:30.738 --> 43:33.436
I even wrote a plan
explaining how you would

43:33.436 --> 43:35.613
get onto this ship
and destroy it,

43:35.613 --> 43:38.006
but you don't need any
of that now,

43:38.006 --> 43:40.835
because I am going to kill
the Greys myself.

43:40.835 --> 43:44.491
So I should do what, just
stay home, watch a ball game?

43:44.491 --> 43:45.927
Oh.

43:45.927 --> 43:48.887
I mean, you could come and
observe, take pictures.

43:48.887 --> 43:51.890
It will make for a nice memory.

43:51.890 --> 43:53.500
What the hell?

43:53.500 --> 43:54.588
Where is it?

43:54.588 --> 43:56.329
I do not know.

43:56.329 --> 43:59.114
Some son of a bitch
snuck in after I was asleep

43:59.114 --> 44:01.160
and stole my bomb.

44:03.379 --> 44:06.818
<i>♪ I can't seem
to face up to the facts ♪</i>

44:06.818 --> 44:10.778
<i>♪ I'm tense and nervous,
and I can't relax ♪</i>

44:10.778 --> 44:15.000
<i>♪ I can't sleep
'cause my bed's on fire ♪</i>

44:15.000 --> 44:19.308
<i>♪ Don't touch me,
I'm a real live wire ♪</i>

44:19.308 --> 44:21.354
<i>♪ Psycho killer</i>

44:21.354 --> 44:22.877
<i>♪ Qu'est-ce que c'est?</i>

44:22.877 --> 44:26.794
<i>♪ Fa-fa-fa-fa,
fa-fa-fa-fa-fa-fa better ♪</i>

44:26.794 --> 44:28.491
<i>♪ Run, run, run, run</i>

44:28.491 --> 44:32.539
<i>♪ Run, run, run away</i>

44:32.539 --> 44:34.976
<i>♪ Oh</i>

44:34.976 --> 44:36.935
<i>♪ Psycho killer</i>

44:36.935 --> 44:38.458
<i>♪ Qu'est-ce que c'est?</i>

44:38.458 --> 44:42.288
<i>♪ Fa-fa-fa-fa-,
fa-fa-fa-fa-fa-fa better ♪</i>

44:42.288 --> 44:44.159
<i>♪ Run, run, run, run</i>

44:44.159 --> 44:48.076
<i>♪ Run, run, run away</i>

44:48.076 --> 44:51.514
<i>♪ Oh oh oh oh</i>

